&lt;div class=&quot;thumbinner mp-thumb&quot; style=&quot;background: transparent; border: none; padding: 0; max-width: 121px;&quot;&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/File:MK37723_Tenzin_Gyatso.jpg&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; title=&quot;14th Dalai Lama&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;14th Dalai Lama&quot; src=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/41/MK37723_Tenzin_Gyatso.jpg/121px-MK37723_Tenzin_Gyatso.jpg&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot; width=&quot;121&quot; height=&quot;161&quot; srcset=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/41/MK37723_Tenzin_Gyatso.jpg/182px-MK37723_Tenzin_Gyatso.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/41/MK37723_Tenzin_Gyatso.jpg/242px-MK37723_Tenzin_Gyatso.jpg 2x&quot; data-file-width=&quot;1936&quot; data-file-height=&quot;2581&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;thumbcaption&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0.25em 0; word-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;14th Dalai Lama&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1796&quot; title=&quot;1796&quot;&gt;1796&lt;/a&gt; – &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/French_Revolutionary_Wars&quot; title=&quot;French Revolutionary Wars&quot;&gt;French Revolutionary Wars&lt;/a&gt;: French forces defeated the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Habsburg_Monarchy&quot; title=&quot;Habsburg Monarchy&quot;&gt;Austrians&lt;/a&gt; at the &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Battle_of_Arcole&quot; title=&quot;Battle of Arcole&quot;&gt;Battle of Arcole&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; in a manoeuvre to cut the latter's line of retreat.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1950&quot; title=&quot;1950&quot;&gt;1950&lt;/a&gt; – The &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/14th_Dalai_Lama&quot; title=&quot;14th Dalai Lama&quot;&gt;14th Dalai Lama&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; &lt;i&gt;(pictured)&lt;/i&gt; assumed full temporal power as ruler of &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Tibet&quot; title=&quot;Tibet&quot;&gt;Tibet&lt;/a&gt; at the age of fifteen.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1968&quot; title=&quot;1968&quot;&gt;1968&lt;/a&gt; – &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/NBC&quot; title=&quot;NBC&quot;&gt;NBC&lt;/a&gt; controversially &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Heidi_Game&quot; title=&quot;Heidi Game&quot;&gt;cut away&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; from an American football game between the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/History_of_the_Oakland_Raiders&quot; title=&quot;History of the Oakland Raiders&quot;&gt;Oakland Raiders&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/New_York_Jets&quot; title=&quot;New York Jets&quot;&gt;New York Jets&lt;/a&gt; to broadcast &lt;i&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Heidi_(1968_film)&quot; title=&quot;Heidi (1968 film)&quot;&gt;Heidi&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/i&gt;, causing viewers in the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Eastern_United_States&quot; title=&quot;Eastern United States&quot;&gt;Eastern United States&lt;/a&gt; to miss the game's dramatic ending.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/2009&quot; title=&quot;2009&quot;&gt;2009&lt;/a&gt; – Administrators at the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/University_of_East_Anglia&quot; title=&quot;University of East Anglia&quot;&gt;University of East Anglia&lt;/a&gt;'s &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Climatic_Research_Unit&quot; title=&quot;Climatic Research Unit&quot;&gt;Climatic Research Unit&lt;/a&gt; discovered that their servers had been &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Security_hacker&quot; title=&quot;Security hacker&quot;&gt;hacked&lt;/a&gt; and thousands of emails and files on &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Climate_change&quot; title=&quot;Climate change&quot;&gt;climate change&lt;/a&gt; &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Climatic_Research_Unit_email_controversy&quot; title=&quot;Climatic Research Unit email controversy&quot;&gt;had been stolen&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;hlist hlist-separated&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0.5em;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Nikephoros_Melissenos&quot; title=&quot;Nikephoros Melissenos&quot;&gt;Nikephoros Melissenos&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;died&quot;&gt;d.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;1104)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Charlotte_of_Mecklenburg-Strelitz&quot; title=&quot;Charlotte of Mecklenburg-Strelitz&quot;&gt;Charlotte of Mecklenburg-Strelitz&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;died&quot;&gt;d.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;1818)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Petra_Burka&quot; title=&quot;Petra Burka&quot;&gt;Petra Burka&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;born&quot;&gt;b.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;1946)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;margin-top: 0.5em;&quot;&gt;
More anniversaries: &lt;div class=&quot;hlist hlist-separated inline nowraplinks&quot;&gt;
