		<summary type="html">&lt;div class=&quot;mw-parser-output&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/November_23&quot; title=&quot;November 23&quot;&gt;November 23&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;: &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Labor_Thanksgiving_Day&quot; title=&quot;Labor Thanksgiving Day&quot;&gt;Labor Thanksgiving Day&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; in Japan
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;float:right;margin-left:0.5em;&quot; id=&quot;mp-otd-img&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;thumbinner mp-thumb&quot; style=&quot;background: transparent; border: none; padding: 0; max-width: 124px;&quot;&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/File:Edwin-hubble.jpg&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; title=&quot;Edwin Hubble&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Edwin Hubble&quot; src=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e5/Edwin-hubble.jpg/124px-Edwin-hubble.jpg&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot; width=&quot;124&quot; height=&quot;159&quot; srcset=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e5/Edwin-hubble.jpg/186px-Edwin-hubble.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/e/e5/Edwin-hubble.jpg 2x&quot; data-file-width=&quot;196&quot; data-file-height=&quot;251&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;thumbcaption&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0.25em 0; word-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;Edwin Hubble&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1733&quot; title=&quot;1733&quot;&gt;1733&lt;/a&gt; – African slaves in the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Danish_West_Indies&quot; title=&quot;Danish West Indies&quot;&gt;Danish West Indies&lt;/a&gt; began &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1733_slave_insurrection_on_St._John&quot; title=&quot;1733 slave insurrection on St. John&quot;&gt;an insurrection&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; in one of the earliest and longest &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Slave_rebellion&quot; title=&quot;Slave rebellion&quot;&gt;slave revolts&lt;/a&gt; in the Americas.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1867&quot; title=&quot;1867&quot;&gt;1867&lt;/a&gt; – The &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Manchester_Martyrs&quot; title=&quot;Manchester Martyrs&quot;&gt;Manchester Martyrs&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; were hanged in &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Manchester&quot; title=&quot;Manchester&quot;&gt;Manchester&lt;/a&gt;, England, for killing a police officer while helping two &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Irish_nationalism&quot; title=&quot;Irish nationalism&quot;&gt;Irish nationalists&lt;/a&gt; escape from police custody.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1924&quot; title=&quot;1924&quot;&gt;1924&lt;/a&gt; – &lt;i&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/The_New_York_Times&quot; title=&quot;The New York Times&quot;&gt;The New York Times&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/i&gt; published evidence from &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Edwin_Hubble&quot; title=&quot;Edwin Hubble&quot;&gt;Edwin Hubble&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; &lt;i&gt;(pictured)&lt;/i&gt; stating that the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Andromeda_Galaxy&quot; title=&quot;Andromeda Galaxy&quot;&gt;Andromeda Nebula&lt;/a&gt;, previously believed to be part of the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Milky_Way&quot; title=&quot;Milky Way&quot;&gt;Milky Way&lt;/a&gt;, is in fact another galaxy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1976&quot; title=&quot;1976&quot;&gt;1976&lt;/a&gt; – &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Jacques_Mayol&quot; title=&quot;Jacques Mayol&quot;&gt;Jacques Mayol&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; became the first person to &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Freediving&quot; title=&quot;Freediving&quot;&gt;freedive&lt;/a&gt; to a depth of 100 metres (330&amp;#160;ft).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/2011&quot; title=&quot;2011&quot;&gt;2011&lt;/a&gt; – &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Arab_Spring&quot; title=&quot;Arab Spring&quot;&gt;Arab Spring&lt;/a&gt;: After &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Yemeni_Revolution&quot; title=&quot;Yemeni Revolution&quot;&gt;11 months of protests in Yemen&lt;/a&gt;, President &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Ali_Abdullah_Saleh&quot; title=&quot;Ali Abdullah Saleh&quot;&gt;Ali Abdullah Saleh&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; agreed to transfer power to Vice President &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Abdrabbuh_Mansur_Hadi&quot; title=&quot;Abdrabbuh Mansur Hadi&quot;&gt;Abdrabbuh Mansur Hadi&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;hlist hlist-separated&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0.5em;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Beatriz_Galindo&quot; title=&quot;Beatriz Galindo&quot;&gt;Beatriz Galindo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;died&quot;&gt;d.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;1535)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/El_Lissitzky&quot; title=&quot;El Lissitzky&quot;&gt;El Lissitzky&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;born&quot;&gt;b.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;1890)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Mary_Whitehouse&quot; title=&quot;Mary Whitehouse&quot;&gt;Mary Whitehouse&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;died&quot;&gt;d.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;2001)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;margin-top: 0.5em;&quot;&gt;
More anniversaries: &lt;div class=&quot;hlist hlist-separated inline nowraplinks&quot;&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/November_22&quot; title=&quot;November 22&quot;&gt;November 22&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
